Project: Responsive Blog Website - Frontend
Files included below. Create these files in a project folder (e.g., /responsive-blog-frontend):
  - index.html       (main page + single post template)
  - styles.css      (styles)
  - script.js       (JS for mobile menu, search, demo content)

Open index.html in a browser. No build tools required.
-->

